        </div>
        <div class="text-center right_content paddinft30">
          <h2>#Empties4Good just got better</h2>
          <p>Our unique #Empties4Good  feature, allows you to not only reduce environmental damage but also reduces how much you’d spend on your next purchase.</p>
          <p>For every empty you send us, we reward you with 500 Plum reward points i.e. Rs. 50 in shopping credits on plumgoodness.com!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rewards-faq">
    <div class="container">
      {% section 'rewards-faq' %}
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
